        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "to process all the 1003 vector elements:\n      One would need to launch 16 thread blocks However, the 16 thread blocks would have 1024 threads. We need to disable the last 21 threads in thread block 15 from doing work not expected/allowed by the original program. Keep in mind that these 16 blocks are partitioned into 32 warps. Only the last warp will have control divergence.",
            "position": {
              "start": { "line": 24, "column": 1, "offset": 1023 },
              "end": { "line": 25, "column": 337, "offset": 1400 },
